You see a strange man, he appears to be from out of town.

"Hello, I don't suppose you have any ocean sprouts do you?
I love those ocean sprouts. They don't sell them here. I'd pay you
40 gold if you could get one."

"I have a friend who used to sell those on the beach. She might be moving soon though. If we could find her, it might be easy money." Mary Says.

Do you accept the Quest?